💬 CHATBOT INTEGRATION:

The chatbot loads automatically when you open index.html!

How it works:
   1. chatbot-loader.js runs
   2. Loads chatbot.html content
   3. Adds chat button to page
   4. Ready to chat!

To use chatbot alone:
   - Open chatbot.html directly
   - Standalone version

