🚀 DEPLOYMENT OPTIONS:

1. Any Web Host:
   - Upload via FTP
   - Set index.html as homepage
   
2. GitHub Pages (FREE):
   - Create GitHub repo
   - Upload files
   - Enable Pages
   - Get free HTTPS URL!

3. Netlify (FREE):
   - Drag folder to Netlify
   - Instant deployment
   - Custom domain support

4. Your Current Host:
   - Replace old files
   - Keep same URL
   - Instant upgrade!

